content:
Manage Work with Omni Inbox

To access Omni Inbox in the Salesforce Mobile app, log in with your Salesforce credentials and click Menu | All Items | Omni Inbox (Beta).

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
Messaging Agent

To view work items, change your presence status to indicate you're available.

To resume previously assigned or paused work, tap the work item.
To accept new work, tap the checkmark next to the work item.
To decline work, tap the X next to the work item (if allowed by admin).

SEE ALSO
